comment: * The Attributes.Name class represents an attribute name stored in * this Map. Valid attribute names are case-insensitive, are restricted * to the ASCII characters in the set [0-9a-zA-Z_-], and cannot exceed * 70 characters in length. Attribute values can contain any characters * and will be UTF8-encoded when written to the output stream. See the * JAR File Specification * for more information about valid attribute names and values.
